num=int(input("Enter any number"))
s=0
while(num!=0):
    rem=num%10
    s=(s*10)+rem
    num=num//10
print("The Reverse number is",s)

output:

========================================================== RESTART: C:/Users/win/AppData/Local/Programs/Python/Python39/reverse.py =========================================================
Enter any number 1234
The Reverse number is 4321
>>> 
